### ================== RUTAS CON AUTENTICACIÓN ==================

### Obtener todos los vendedores (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ocul/Sellers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener vendedor por ID (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ocul/Sellers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear un nuevo vendedor (CON token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ocul/Sellers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Global Imports",
  "email": "contact@globalimports.co",
  "phone": "3209876543",
  "password": "strongpassword456",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Actualizar un vendedor (CON token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/ocul/Sellers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "3215550102"
}

### Eliminar un vendedor físicamente (CON token)
